sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 普通用户
    participant Controller as Dish/OrderController
    participant Service as OrderService
    participant DB as MySQL
    participant Redis as Redis缓存

    User->>Controller: 浏览菜品列表
    Controller->>Redis: 查询热点菜品缓存
    alt 缓存命中
        Redis-->>Controller: 返回菜品数据
    else 缓存未命中
        Controller->>DB: 查询菜品表
        DB-->>Controller: 返回数据
        Controller->>Redis: 写入缓存
    end
    Controller-->>User: 展示菜品
    
    User->>Controller: 提交订单 (createOrder)
    Controller->>Service: 创建订单记录
    Service->>DB: 插入 order 表
    DB-->>Service: 返回订单ID
    Service-->>Controller: 下单成功
    Controller-->>User: 反馈结果
